column5: NOt sure if this has been posted yet...you have to watch some commercials first, Dave hits the screen at 4 minutes.  http://www.myoutdoortv.com/video/video.php...vHtMY_NNSBltI2E
Thanks for the link. It's 1st aired on Thanksgiving. Brings back some good memoires of fishing with Pete.  -Dave
WTG Dave     Great job  Sure looked like you guys had a super time catching them big gators Thanks for link scuro2
They didn't mention that you don't have to tip the guides, either.
Great job handling those pike! Is this what you did as a summer job or something?
great show to bad these guys dont tip there guides though.  great job dave!!!!  Cheers!
I love this episode.  I did not realize this was you.  Nice going!
cool nice job Ramble! congrats on your pikin adventures with Pete, seems like a great guy to fish with, looks like you had a blast...   Hawk
Pete is great. It's nice to fish with someone who has the same sence of humour you do. Helps that he cusses about as much as i do too lol.  -Dave
Awsome video, thats so cool to be a guide up there. Great tool you made. I know what its for, but can you explain it? How it differs from the long pliers?  Dirk....
